search_results.title: Kika Dorsey | English
search_results.snippet: Kika Dorsey is a CU lecturer and author in Boulder, Colorado. She has a PhD in Comparative Literature and her books include the chapbook Beside Herself.

search_results.title: Bio
search_results.snippet: Kika Dorsey is an author and a Lecturer at the University of Colorado, Boulder. She teaches literature and creative writing classes.
